query:
/*+  */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from site AS s
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('askubuntu',
'math') AND t1.name IN ('algebraic-curves',
'differential-forms',
'epsilon-delta',
'filesystem',
'software-center',
'stochastic-integrals')
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND u1.reputation >= 10 AND u1.reputation <= 100000
inner join question AS q1
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND q1.id = a1.question_id AND q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 10 AND q1.view_count <= 1000
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Constituent',
'Custodian',
'Editor',
'Excavator',
'Revival',
'Supporter') group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
